{"tid":1466861,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民間記招應該點講今晚機場件事？","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:53:01.000Z","uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d6b8ff43f2819d297480209efe25fc5ce151d4","tid":1466861,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664ed32e0c73bfb144ba87a5962ee8ca6bef0632","tid":1466861,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:37.000Z","msg":"用返港台訪問手足所講的野就得？<br />\n<br />\n手足話見到佢着住反光衣喺到影人大頭<br />\n然後手足問佢係咪記者<br />\n佢乜都冇講即刻走<br />\n手足追住佢 㩒低左佢之後<br />\n佢就話自己係tourist(的確係用英文講)<br />\n手足就搜佢個袋 但搵唔到記者證<br />\n搵到護照，一本筆記簿，寫住我♡警察定唔知I♡警察的衫"},{"pid":"10f5eb8d2bdf00e88e73c871a9fe9dec8523b8f5","tid":1466861,"uid":233228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:10.000Z","msg":"勇敢同被打嘅人道歉啦<br />\n無論點打人都係錯"},{"pid":"98a7ae871eb475438cf77c6a4c14d0a0a23e7dc1","tid":1466861,"uid":87735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:21:52.000Z","msg":"個問題咪就係基於警隊被揭法滲入臥底扮示威者引發暴力事件<br />\n同警方過度武力有違國際標準等令抗爭者行動升級<br />\n行政長官仍然沒有合適回應及處理讓社會怒潮平伏"},{"pid":"2fe6d92dd3eb3adab15c5821bf0f165c39d9a182","tid":1466861,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:44:20.000Z","msg":"道歉似乎係最好"},{"pid":"5218f3a24d7344633e7468ec8107545f26b042cd","tid":1466861,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:45:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"835132fb8009da9e47f0c41d04243c741b73b706","tid":1466861,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:45:57.000Z","msg":"道歉既話勇武會唔會插佢地"},{"pid":"85cb189673a2843a5a0a54c7ab80d189cd865af5","tid":1466861,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:53:01.000Z","msg":"我覺得一黎就同琴日受影響既旅客道左歉先 係最好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我地阻礙旅客上機 係要